"tid":406431,"uid":32588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:56:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我識人係因為食藥食到肥，佢地自己都唔想</blockquote><br />\n食咩藥會肥到成隻豬咁呀？<br />\n一睇你個名就知唔簡單</blockquote><br />\n類固醇都會食到肥"},{"pid":"a6f52402879a8e3af067c567894e18d3917fe9e3","tid":406431,"uid":33874,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"成日話肥婆迫你，其實佢地都好慘嫁<br />\n知唔知肥婆要坐低起身要消耗幾大運動量？<br />\n係ikea見過，有兩個肥婆試梳化，我就坐佢前面嗰張<br />\n大肥坐低<br />\n大肥：仆街，張野軟既，我起唔返身<br />\n小肥聽完就拉起大肥，點知大肥太重坐埋落去。搵個職員黎拉，個女職員話拉唔起，叫咪搵左兩個男職員黎，佢叫咪嗰下我聽到周邊啲人係咁笑<br />\n其實肥婆坐低真係好大心理陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274fffaaf1000c711929999e640c2ebca77cf377","tid":406431,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:00:50.000Z","msg":"霸左三個人既位 俾一個人價錢"},{"pid":"fb3bec0ed91a2f113a40c851e9d9fcac67f061c5","tid":406431,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日話肥婆迫你，其實佢地都好慘嫁<br />\n知唔知肥婆要坐低起身要消耗幾大運動量？<br />\n係ikea見過，有兩個肥婆試梳化，我就坐佢前面嗰張<br />\n大肥坐低<br />\n大肥：仆街，張野軟既，我起唔返身<br />\n小肥聽完就拉起大肥，點知大肥太重坐埋落去。搵個職員黎拉，個女職員話拉唔起，叫咪搵左兩個男職員黎，佢叫咪嗰下我聽到周邊啲人係咁笑<br />\n其實肥婆坐低真係好大心理陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb6c88b6d8ee29c4a6c9ebec003d1db90d3797c","tid":406431,"uid":85906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我識人係因為食藥食到肥，佢地自己都唔想</blockquote><br />\n食咩藥會肥到成隻豬咁呀？<br />\n一睇你個名就知唔簡單</blockquote><br />\n類固醇都會食到肥</blockquote><br />\n我就係由細食到大所以由細肥到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我想講其實真係減得返 我都努力緊"},{"pid":"1517763a3e9fad2b3f42fe6c397b9c2369a851bb","tid":406431,"uid":93202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"嗰朝番工唔係好舒服<br />\n狗鐵難得有位坐 <br />\n我都覺得好奇怪, 成班阿叔阿嬸竟然企係度唔坐?<br />\n我太攰又暈暈地咪唔諗咁多坐落去<br />\n屌 中伏<br />\n<br />\n原來隔離係個死肥西, 坐之前竟然睇唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐落去即刻感覺到有條脂肪比壓逼住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n騎虎難下都係照坐左成程車 因為太唔舒服同埋企起身好老尷<br />\n結果逼足左半粒鐘<br />\n最仆街係 <br />\n停左站再開車嗰下咪會有後衝力 <br />\n條肥婆仲要完全無避忌咁諗住卸晒啲力落黎<br />\n我係咁搵個背囊頂住佢 佢先識縮少少 我仆佢個臭街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bcbdd79e16bac80f48840539ef308dabdddcf9","tid":406431,"uid":66925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:22:33.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 煙無墳 )<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"644ed1ea32070e3804e4729aeae30184214a3bf8","tid":406431,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:24:36.000Z","msg":"到底肥婆幾撚時絕種"},{"pid":"cf28882d8de07eeef11e26b224635766b15d5c98","tid":406431,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"sorry 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e86ef352f8213970cba27f1566089dc4cbb270e","tid":406431,"uid":63458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:28:43.000Z","msg":"對air就快俾佢踩爛"},{"pid":"7ef040fd3ae0771f31acd535f889568c41693c38","tid":406431,"uid":6623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:31:33.000Z","msg":"已經唔係一般嘅肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5401fceb632519a55c165151a2b01b7bf2af297f","tid":406431,"uid":77972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:52:22.000Z","msg":"右邊就坐左個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好撚噁心<br />\n一身油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2391ff0585fa2bc7d6446c47ecd266ebdad5d50","tid":406431,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我識人係因為食藥食到肥，佢地自己都唔想</blockquote><br />\n食咩藥會肥到成隻豬咁呀？<br />\n一睇你個名就知唔簡單</blockquote><br />\n無知真可怕.....抗抑鬱藥就係其中一個例子"},{"pid":"d0c3d5edfa3bda1f3adb92b93ed5a74c543e3de8","tid":406431,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我識人係因為食藥食到肥，佢地自己都唔想</blockquote><br />\n食咩藥會肥到成隻豬咁呀？<br />\n一睇你個名就知唔簡單</blockquote><br />\n無知真可怕.....抗抑鬱藥就係其中一個例子</blockquote><br />\n屌搞到咁不如死撚左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe29e3420dbf50ce91f395dc9bfb595c4f382ce7","tid":406431,"uid":70538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我識人係因為食藥食到肥，佢地自己都唔想</blockquote><br />\n食咩藥會肥到成隻豬咁呀？<br />\n一睇你個名就知唔簡單</blockquote><br />\n無知真可怕.....抗抑鬱藥就係其中一個例子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗見到自己食藥食到咁肥， 應該會抑鬱。"},{"pid":"505c8bb30b6a85bdb6cd9e6d7d5351b54e4db5cd","tid":406431,"uid":99805,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:06:44.000Z","msg":"連登仔有無咁膚淺<br />\n抑鬱可能體型問題引起,但食抑鬱藥食到肥既,本身會唔會係體型問題?<br />\n關體型事佢食減肥藥得啦,洗撚食抑鬱藥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}